What is this?

This notebook details the results of simulating the 2022 college football season before any actual games are played.

1 2022 Week 0 Team Ratings

The following table displays each teams Rating, which is a combination of their previous seasons Elo Rating, offensive efficiency, defensive efficiency, and a moving average of their composite recruiting score. These ratings are Week 0 ratings because they rely only on information from previous seasons. As the season progresses, these ratings will update for each team as we gain new information based on the results of games (with the exception of recruiting, which is computed at the yearly level).
